subject: Cancellation Confirmed — {{ booking_id }}
<h2>Booking Cancelled</h2>
<p>Dear {{ customer_name }},</p>
<p>Your booking <strong>{{ booking_id }}</strong> at {{ hub_name }} has been cancelled.</p>
<p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{ reason }}</p>
<p><strong>Refund Amount:</strong> {{ refund_amount }}</p>
<p>If you have any questions, please contact {{ hub_name }} directly.</p>
